-.TP
-\fB--json\fR \fB<fields>\fR
-Output JSON with the specified fields
-
-.TP
-\fB-L\fR, \fB--limit\fR \fB<int> (default 20)\fR
-Maximum number of runs to fetch
-
-.TP
-\fB-s\fR, \fB--status\fR \fB<string>\fR
